Comment: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:02.38,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Go ask my instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:23.72,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一直响着的沉默的警铃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:25.94,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}那又是谁的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:28.54,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不要迷茫跳进去跳进去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.54,0:01:30.90,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}站起来 破坏掉这无理的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:32.49,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果解不开这沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:34.91,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就大喊露鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:37.24,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}直到终幕我都要说
